<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٧ - مَسْأَلَة<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>الْمُعْتَكف إِذا احْتَلَمَ وَأمكنهُ الْغسْل فِي الْمَسْجِد عذر فِي الْخُرُوج<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>